Package: hte
Type: Package
Title: Heterogeneous Treatment Effect Estimator Using Random Forests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Allen Tang
Maintainer: Allen Tang <actang.me@gmail.com>
Description: Estimate heterogeneous treatment effects in experimental and 
    observational studies with application ranging from personalized medicine 
    to online advertisement recommendation systems. Implement a number of 
    algorithms that are based on random forest to estimate the conditional 
    average treatment effect (CATE) function.
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.9), foreach, doParallel, plyr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
SystemRequirements: C++11
